.br

.h1 "EXAMPLE"
.P
To highlight code blocks in a document with ANSI escape sequences:
.nl
.PP
.in 10
mkcat README.md | mkhigh \-o esc | mkout
.br

.P
To highlight code blocks for a standalone HTML page:
.nl
.PP
.in 10
mkcat README.md | mkhigh | mkpage | mkhtml > README.html
.br

